title: See the Fisher-Price® Revolve Swing in action! | Fisher-Price
description: Give your arms a much-needed break and see how the Fisher-Price® Revolve Swing’s unique blend of circular and swinging motions, inspired by mom’s natural movements, can help soothe your baby in familiar way. The only baby swing with this distinctive motion, the Revolve Swing also comes with six speed options, a variety of calming music and sounds, and an overhead mobile to entertain your little one. And its sleek frame takes up 25 percent less floor space than other swings, too!

transcripts: Meet Revolve Swing. With a revolutionary blend of motion inspired by mom's natural movement. Introducing the revolve swing. Unlike other swings that go back and forth, the revolve swing combines circular and swivel motions to soothe your baby in a uniquely familiar way.  So your little one can relax and you have more time for everything else. the revolve swing, only from Fisher Price.
